: : Rodimus Prime/Kup : :

Rodimus was looking over files in his computer when the room was filled with a flash of light. The Commander turns around in his chair to look out the large window. All he could see was the last of what seemd to be a fire trail going down in the hills north of the base.

Rodimus Prime: What on Cybertron was that?!

Meanwhile in the control room Kup was still at the sensor station when it picked up a signal. It was close and fast. The station started a siren and started to flash alert lights.

Kup had been paying little attention to the screens and the alarms and lights caused him to jump, nearly falling out of his chair. He gets back up and tries to ID what the trouble was.

Kup: What in the bloody hell?! If this is the Predacons I&#39;m going to incenerate their hides!

Kup then figured out what had happaned, from the sensor data.

Kup was about to contact Rodimus when the Commander&#39;s voice came over the comm system.

Rodimus Prime: Prime to control room, what&#39;s goind on? Did you pick up that activity outside?

Kup hit a button so he could reply.

Kup: We picked it up alright, Sir. It scared the hell out of me! The sensors read it as some sort of crystalized structure. Want me to go check it out?

Rodimus Prime: Not alone, old timer, I&#39;m coming also. I&#39;ll be right there.

Kup: Old timer?! Why I oughta... Your getting pretty old yourself Rody...

Kup was cut off as the comm link was closed.

Kup waited for Rodimus to arrive.

Rodimus stepped out of his office and started to walk to the control room.
